content.rendered:
Directed by Akiv Ali.

Written by Surabhi Bhatnagar. Tarun Jain. Luv Ranjan.

Cast Ajay Devgn(Aashish). Tabu(Manju). Rakul Preet Singh(Ayesha). Jimmy Shergill(V.K (as Jimmy Sheirgill)). Alok Nath(Dada). Madhumalti Kapoor(Veerendra’s wife – Dadi). Bhavin Bhanushali(Ishaan Mehra). Gandharv Dewan(Hasmukh (V.K’s Assistant)). Kumud Mishra(Atul). Sunny Singh(Akash (as Sunny Singh Nijjar)). Inayat Sood(Ishita Mehra). Minhaz Zee(Johny Singh). Jaaved Jaaferi(Sameer (as Javed Jaffrey)). Nadine Payne(Lily). Rajveer Singh(Rishi Saxena). Harry Anton(Aysha’s Date). Radhika Bangia(Ayesha’s friend). Samantha Sharon Watson(Alice (Receptionist)). Vincent Woods(Nerdy Man (as Vince Woods)).Hussain Dalal. Alex Bonsu(Thug #1). Kevin Daniels(Thug #2). Richard Smithee(Thug #3). Kajal Thangjam(Maid). Daniel Maya(Waiter and Barman). Ryan Valmont(Barman). Karishma Karpal(Bride). Gulnaaz Khan(Vaddi Sharaban Party Dancer). Teena Paradkar(Vaddi Sharaban Party Dancer). Nisha George(Vaddi Sharaban Party Dancer). Sammy Jonas Heaney(Vaddi Sharaban Party Dancer (as Sammy John Heaney)). Manoj Anand(Vaddi Sharaban Party Guest). Priya Tailor(Vaddi Sharaban Party Guest). Kuldeep N.(Vaddi Sharaban Party Guest). Anisha Mandhara(Vaddi Sharaban Party Guest). Soni Marwah(Vaddi Sharaban Party Guest). Frina Mehta(Vaddi Sharaban Party Guest).

Language Hindi.

Producers Inderjit Chadha. Ankur Garg. Bhushan Kumar. Krishan Kumar. Sanjay Mehta. Ronak Motla. Luv Ranjan. Ravi Sarin. Sudipto Sarkar.

Production Luv Films. T-Series.
